      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "NITRO'S RUBY (1) has a fair record and proved too strong last time to win by 2.75 lengths at this track in a handy 17.26 beating Zeta Prime. Can make it back-to-back wins. ERAMOSA (3) boasts a strong record this journey here with five wins and six minors from 12 tries. Scored by half a length last time (17.17) in a Grade 5 over 300m at this track. Makes strong appeal on best. MAD HOWLER (6) was racing in great form recording two on end before he was checked in the run and placed in a Grade 3/4 at this track (17.36). Worth following up. RAPIDO PRONTO (7) scored last time and appeals as a top-three prospect.",
